item.description:
Meet Other singles (25-45) at The Cabby Shack.

Single Mingle Cocktail hour 7-9pm ....Ice Breakers, Music & fun

All you have to do is get yourself there -- let us do the rest! Our job is to get you mingling and meeting other like-minded people.

No more awkward opening lines! Let us take the pain (and the shyness) out of making new friends, a lover, a soul-mate... Who knows?

9pm-1 am - Stick around after the cocktail hour and Cabby's opens to the public, for live music by Joe's Fish Sandwich - a high-energy cover band that will have you up and dancing before you finish your first drink.

There's a DJ to play between sets, so the music never stops!

What's guaranteed is great music, lots of fun, and the very real possiblity of making a date with a special someone.

Space is limited, so sign up now!
